{"parse":{"title":"Figluster's Mudfish","pageid":111981,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||8}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_41\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=27435\n|ilvl=60\n|name=Figluster's Mudfish}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nCan be fished from [[Nagrand]]'s rivers and lakes. Pools can be found throughout the same areas.\n\nShares pool spawn locations with [[Pure Water]] and [[Icefin Bluefish]].\n\n==Figluster's Mudfish as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Grilled Mudfish}}\n\n== Patch changes ==\n{{Patch 2.0.1|note=Added in [[Burning Crusade]].}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|27435}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/figlusters_mudfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]"}}}